--- !u!1001 &70758624
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.size
      value: 66
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: MC leaves the workshop through the servant passage, the broken gold
        gear hidden beneath his coat.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Behind him, the manor remains warm and alive.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: A house continuing without him.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: He crosses the west garden.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: The fog has thickened around the trees. The path to the rear gate is
        nearly swallowed by it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[5]'
      value: Then he sees it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[6]'
      value: A parcel rests on the stone bench beneath the garden lantern, wrapped
        in dark paper and bound with black cord.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[7]'
      value: No messenger waits nearby.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[8]'
      value: No footsteps lead away.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[9]'
      value: MC approaches slowly.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[10]'
      value: 'MC: Another gift.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[11]'
      value: The parcel bears no name.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[12]'
      value: Only the crest of House Ashworth, pressed into a gold seal.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[13]'
      value: MC breaks the seal and opens it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[14]'
      value: Inside are three folded papers, held together by a narrow strip of black
        ribbon.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[15]'
      value: The first is a travel authorization.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[16]'
      value: 'Travel Authorization: Lord Edmund Ashworth departed House Ashworth
        before dawn.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[17]'
      value: 'Destination: The Registry.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[18]'
      value: 'Route: Eastern rail line, by way of the ironworks.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[19]'
      value: The second is an incident notice.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[20]'
      value: 'Incident Notice:'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[21]'
      value: Eastern line incident.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[22]'
      value: Hour certified.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[23]'
      value: "Admission at Saint Bartholomew\u2019s by first light."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[24]'
      value: The third is marked with a counterstamp from the Court of Continuance.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[25]'
      value: 'Counterstamp:'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[26]'
      value: "Claim of Continuance \u2014 entered that same morning."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[27]'
      value: Filed before the incident notice reached the Court.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[28]'
      value: 'MC: The claim was filed before the accident could have reached them.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[29]'
      value: 'MC: Unless the road was prepared as carefully as the claim.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[30]'
      value: He holds the papers together.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[31]'
      value: "MC: Departed before dawn. The line failed at this hour. Admitted at
        Saint Bartholomew\u2019s by first light."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[32]'
      value: 'MC: One route. One hour.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[33]'
      value: 'MC: The Court will call that one man.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[34]'
      value: 'MC (quieter): Best that person be me.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[35]'
      value: The words do not comfort him as much as they should.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[36]'
      value: A sound comes from the trees.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[37]'
      value: Not footsteps.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[38]'
      value: A cane touching wet stone.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[39]'
      value: MC turns.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[40]'
      value: Beyond the lantern light, the other man waits beneath the branches,
        half hidden by the fog.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[41]'
      value: 'MC: You left this for me.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[42]'
      value: 'Other Him: I did.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[43]'
      value: 'MC: Why?'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[44]'
      value: Other Him does not come closer.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[45]'
      value: 'Other Him: Because memory can be doubted.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[46]'
      value: He looks toward the manor.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[47]'
      value: 'Other Him: A body can be remade.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[48]'
      value: A pause.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[49]'
      value: 'Other Him: But a life must arrive somewhere.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[50]'
      value: MC steps toward him.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[51]'
      value: 'MC: What does that mean?'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[52]'
      value: 'Other Him: Bring the parcel to the Trial.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[53]'
      value: 'MC: Stop running from me.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[54]'
      value: 'Other Him: I am not running from you.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[55]'
      value: The words are almost lost in the fog.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[56]'
      value: 'Other Him: Not anymore.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[57]'
      value: A bell begins to toll from the Court district.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[58]'
      value: Once.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[59]'
      value: Then again.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[60]'
      value: The hour before dawn.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[61]'
      value: MC looks toward the sound.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[62]'
      value: When he turns back, the other man is gone.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[63]'
      value: MC stands alone in the west garden, holding the counterstamped papers
        beneath the lantern.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[64]'
      value: The third proof has been found.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 159193195069834464, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[65]'
      value: Chronology Proof.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4486140054593480548, guid: 6f0364fa11fbb4f65ab2d575e1887af4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: TextCrawlScreen
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
